Development of version 1.0 - 2.0:
---------------------------------
- Getting currently used themes (like icon-,window-themes or backgrounds) and save them to a theme package
 - The theme package is a gzipped package (with a version information file) that contains all previously collected themes.
- Theme and package installation by Drag and Drop (maybe asking what theme has been choosen if it is not recognized)
- Dividing the attributes from CTheme
#-> Completing this tasks leads to version 1.0
- More and more integration of www.Gnome-Look.org (Hintergründe)
#-> This will continue to count the version numbers up


